### Health Check
GET http://localhost/health

### Sign Up
POST http://localhost/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Sign In
POST http://localhost/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### Reset Password (replace TOKEN with real token from server logs)
POST http://localhost/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "TOKEN",
  "new_password": "newpassword123"
}

### Create User (admin only - replace TOKEN with a valid admin JWT)
POST http://localhost/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

{
  "email": "created@example.com",
  "username": "createduser",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "user"
}

### List Users (admin only - replace TOKEN with a valid admin JWT)
GET http://localhost/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
